      "side": 1,
      "message": "That seems to make an assumption that JSONSchema is about a particular direction, i.e. importing vs exporting, when instead JSONSchema is about the defining the format of a JSON file. The fact that the jsonschema library relied upon the json: tags in the struct is something I consider a feature, not a bug.",
